61
00:05:58,062 --> 00:05:59,606
Tiru itu, Supremo.

62
00:06:02,507 --> 00:06:04,091
Sekurang-kurangnya saya akan berjauhan daripada anda semua

63
00:06:04,232 --> 00:06:05,232
