75
00:06:40,563 --> 00:06:41,564
Sekarang

76
00:06:42,523 --> 00:06:44,192
apa agenda seterusnya?

77
00:08:34,093 --> 00:08:37,054
Awak bernasib baik kerana ini hukuman awak, Cik Shion.

78
00:08:37,835 --> 00:08:41,381
Ingatkan pasti dia akan mengheret awak ke Penjara Neraka Gelap.

79
00:08:42,977 --> 00:08:44,896
Kecewa, Onel?

80
00:08:46,105 --> 00:08:48,107
Saya sakit hati awak mesti fikir macam tu, Cik Shion.

81
00:08:48,733 --> 00:08:50,359
Tapi tidak, tidak kecewa

82
00:08:51,444 --> 00:08:52,612
